{"talk":{"id":72807,"name":"Emily Leproust: How synthetic biology can improve our health, food and materials","description":"What if we could use biology to restore our balance with nature without giving up modern creature comforts? Advocating for a new kind of environmentalism, scientist and entrepreneur Emily Leproust rethinks modern sustainability at the molecular level, using synthetic biology to create green alternatives. From lab-developed insulin and disease-resistant bananas to airplanes made of super-strong spider silk, she explains how reading and writing DNA can lead to groundbreaking innovations in health, food and materials.","slug":"emily_leproust_how_synthetic_biology_can_improve_our_health_food_and_materials","recorded_at":"2020-10-21 00:00:00","published_at":"2021-03-16 14:52:01","updated_at":"2021-09-27 14:57:52","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":655,"name":"TED@BCG"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/f40919ba57bbbebed1ea8b21cd27cac3d03dee96_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/f40919ba57bbbebed1ea8b21cd27cac3d03dee96_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/f40919ba57bbbebed1ea8b21cd27cac3d03dee96_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/f40919ba57bbbebed1ea8b21cd27cac3d03dee96_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/cb97970e916737569a7c4ced97c388a0e7b06283_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/EmilyLeproust_2020S-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":5503171,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/EmilyLeproust_2020S-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":15234805,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/EmilyLeproust_2020S-320k.